Jenna Staples (ジェナ・ステープルズ, Jena Sutēpuruzu) is a member of the Anti-Demon Corps' 8th Unit.


Advertisement
Appearance
Jenna is a young, tall, toned, and voluptuous woman with long hair tied into a side ponytail.

As a member of the 8th Unit, she wears the standard Anti-Demon Corps uniform along with gloves and a neck warmer. Her name and appearance implies she is of western descent.


Advertisement
Personality
Jenna is very outgoing and seems to be an avid manga/anime fan. She appears to have a close relationship with Nei Ookawamura. She shows a bit of a perverted side when she wanted to know more about Yuuki by lightly teasing him with questions about his role in the 7th Unit.

She often has delusions of perverted scenarios which are heavily influenced by the anime she watches.

Her favorite food is meat pie.[1]

Synopsis
Shangri-La Arc
Powers and Abilities
Peach Blessing
Hero (豪剣士ヒーロー, Hīrō, lit. "Strong Swordswoman"): This blessing grants Jenna the strongest shield and sword in the Anti-Demon Corps (she thinks) while also significantly increasing her strength. Her clothing is also changed from her uniform into bikini armor complete with breastplate, thong, gauntlets, greaves, and a domino mask.[2]
